# This folder is referenced by the plugin header's `Domain Path: /languages` directive.
#
# When the plugin is hosted on wordpress.org, translations are auto-loaded from this
# folder by WordPress (since WP 4.6). Translators contribute via translate.wordpress.org
# and their `.po` / `.mo` files land here at install time.
#
# This `.gitkeep` keeps the folder in version control even when no translation file
# exists yet — without it, Plugin Check (and the wp.org reviewers) flag the
# `Domain Path` header as pointing to a non-existent folder.
